io.atomix.copycat.client.response

Interface Response<T extends Response<T>>

  • All Superinterfaces:
    CatalystSerializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractResponse, AcceptResponse, AppendResponse, CommandResponse, ConfigurationResponse, ConfigureResponse, ConnectResponse, InstallResponse, JoinResponse, KeepAliveResponse, LeaveResponse, OperationResponse, PollResponse, PublishResponse, QueryResponse, RegisterResponse, SessionResponse, UnregisterResponse, VoteResponse

    public interface Response<T extends Response<T>>
extends CatalystSerializable
    Base interface for responses.

    Each response has a non-null Response.Status of either Response.Status.OK or Response.Status.ERROR. Responses where status() is Response.Status.ERROR may provide an optional error() code.

    Author:
    Jordan Halterman
